<html lang='en'></html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Account Credentials – FundingHero</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #f5f5f5;
        color: #333;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .banner {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .title {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .description {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .credentials {
        background: #fff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        border: 2px solid #007bff;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .credential-item {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .credential-value {
        color: #6c757d;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .action-button {
        background: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: block;
        cursor: pointer;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .action-button:hover {
        background: #0056b3;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .footer-text {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 12px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .company-name {
        color: #007bff;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      {{#if banner}}
      <img src='{{banner}}' alt='FundingHero Banner' class='banner' />
      {{/if}}

      <div class='greeting'>Hola, <strong>{{email}}</strong></div>
      <div class='title'>Tu cuenta ha sido creada</div>

      <div class='description'>
        Aquí están tus credenciales de acceso. Te recomendamos iniciar sesión y cambiar tu contraseña cuanto antes.
      </div>

      <div style='font-size:large;'><strong>Credenciales:</strong></div>
      <br />
      <div class='credentials'>
        <div class='credential-item'><strong>Email:</strong>
          <span class='credential-value'>{{email}}</span></div>
        <div class='credential-item'><strong>Usuario:</strong>
          <span class='credential-value'>{{username}}</span></div>
        <div class='credential-item'><strong>Contraseña temporal:</strong>
          <span class='credential-value'>{{password}}</span></div>
      </div>

      {{#if landingUrl}}
        <a href='{{landingUrl}}' class='action-button' target='_blank'>Ir al Dashboard</a>
      {{/if}}

      <div class='description' style='font-size:12px;'>
        Por seguridad: no compartas estas credenciales. Si no solicitaste esta cuenta, ignora este mensaje y contáctanos.
      </div>

      <div class='footer-text'>
        Saludos,<br />
        <span class='company-name'>FundingHero</span>
        Team
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
  </html>
